@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199
@tenantSlug = demo

### ✅ Create patient (201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Patient",
  "preferredName": "Johnny",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-03-20",
  "gender": "Male",
  "email": "john.patient@example.com",
  "phoneMobile": "+15559876543",
  "preferredContactMethod": "Mobile",
  "addressLine1": "456 Oak Avenue",
  "city": "Chicago",
  "stateProvince": "IL",
  "postalCode": "60601",
  "countryCode": "US",
  "smsOptIn": true,
  "emailOptIn": true
}

###

### ✅ List patients (200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ✅ Search patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients?search=john&page=1&pageSize=10
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ✅ Get patient by ID (200) — replace {id}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ❌ Patient not found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

###

### ❌ Unauthorized (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients

###

### ❌ Validation error (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": ""
}

###

### 🗑️ Delete patient (204) — replace {id}
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

